data.description: WELCOME TO COTTONWOOD, one of the most desired luxury home communities just outside Milton Florida. Offering 206 custom-built homes, with up to 6 bedrooms and on lots of a half-acre plus. These homes come in all sizes, varying in price from $400,000 to $800,000 or more. The community is gated and secure, offering privacy and peace of mind. Yards and streets are landscaped, with most having part of the backyard bordering mature trees and nature paths. The entrance to Cottonwood on Shamrock and William Norris Rd is a short ride to Highways 89 and 90, which provides easy access to all of Pensacola. Downtown Milton is minutes away, with a Publix and many excellent restaurants and stores. Golfers will love that Tanglewood Golf and Country Club is just a few streets away from Cottonwood as well. With these elegant one-of-a-kind homes, a great location, and in a secure gated neighborhood, Cottonwood has to be one of the best choices to look for your dream home.   Our offered home is a five-bedroom, three-bathroom home, set on a generous half-acre lot within the gated Cottonwood Community. It offers both space and functionality. Its split floor plan provides distinct privacy and ample opportunities for personalization. The property itself boasts a large, flat backyard perfect for a variety of outdoor enhancements, such as a swimming pool and an outdoor kitchen. An additional standout feature is the dedicated pet run equipped with its own septic system, adding a practical aspect to its overall appeal. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity. Contact us now to arrange a personal tour and experience firsthand the potential of this wonderful property in one of the best communities of Milton!
